       <table border="0" width="100%">             
 <tr>             
  <td width="100%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;      
             
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;
line-height:110%"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-size:22.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:方正魏碑简体;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">跳</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:
normal"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes; font-size: 22.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 方正魏碑简体" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span style="font-size:22.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:方正魏碑简体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">舞</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:22.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:方正魏碑简体"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></b></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center;line-height:110%"><span style="font-family:楷体_GB2312">武汉大学日本留学生 
上野纪久子<span lang="EN-US"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:110%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:
12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:110%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">我高中的时候，<u>属于挥动指挥棒跳舞的俱乐部</u></span>
<sup><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">①</span></sup>
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">，我非常喜欢跳舞。高中毕业以后我一直没跳过舞。想跳舞想得不得了，可是因为忙，没有时间，而且也没有机会。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:110%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">来中国武汉大学大概一个半月以后，在房间里我从办公室那儿听到自己感兴趣的音乐和在日本受欢迎的歌，心想：“</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
mso-ascii-font-family:宋体">诶</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">，谁在做什么？”<u>我从窗户瞧瞧</u></span><!--[if supportFields]><sup><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312'><span style='mso-element:field-begin'></span> = 2 \* GB3 <span
style='mso-element:field-separator'></span></span></sup><![endif]-->
<sup><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">②</span></sup><!--[if supportFields]><sup><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312'><span style='mso-element:field-end'></span></span></sup><![endif]-->
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">。发现跳舞的是日本老同学。我高兴极了，想马上去参加。但是我犹豫了。因为我不知道老同学会怎么样？我问一位朋友：“我去参加跳舞，你觉得怎么样？<u>你想老同学会怎么样？</u></span><!--[if supportFields]><sup><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312'><span style='mso-element:field-begin'></span> = 3 \* GB3 <span
style='mso-element:field-separator'></span></span></sup><![endif]-->
<sup><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">③</span></sup><!--[if supportFields]><sup><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312'><span style='mso-element:field-end'></span></span></sup><![endif]-->
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">”朋友说：“没关系吧，老同学一定欢迎你。如果你真的想跳舞，就去吧。”听了朋友的话，我鼓起勇气向办公室走去。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
  <tr>
    <td width="48" height="0"></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td></td>
    <td><img src="images/2000_11/new_pa2.jpg" v:shapes="_x0000_s1026" width="268" height="158"></td>
  </tr>
</table>
</span><!--[if gte vml 1]></o:wrapblock><![endif]-->
<br style="mso-ignore:vglayout" clear="ALL">
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">在这里有几位老同学正合着音乐跳舞。<u>曲子的速度非常快</u></span><!--[if supportFields]><sup><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312'><span style='mso-element:field-begin'></span> = 4 \* GB3 <span
style='mso-element:field-separator'></span></span></sup><![endif]-->
<sup><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">④</span></sup><!--[if supportFields]><sup><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312'><span style='mso-element:field-end'></span></span></sup><![endif]-->
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">，所以跳的速度也非常快。看起来合曲的事很困难，可是她们都很愉快，连看她们的我也非常愉快。然后，我提心吊胆地说：“我也想参加，跟你们一起跳舞，可以吗？”她们说：“当然可以，来吧，来吧！”我无比高兴。因为我盼望已久的事居然意外地实现了，我好不容易又可以跳舞了。我认识到，如果碰到自己想做的事，就应该去争取，不然的话，以后一定后悔。但是为什么她们现在跳舞呢？我问她们，她们说：“我们快要回日本了，所以想给大家留下一个美好的回忆。也许哪一天，我们在什么地方可能跳舞，你一定来吧！”我明白了为什么她们在练舞。因为我不出场正式表演，只练习一起跳。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:110%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">开始练习了。我发现有个人跳舞跳得真棒。这个人就是我们的老师。她叫三津山菜穗，跟这样的人一起跳舞让我高兴。她是很好的老师。<u>曲子的速度很快</u></span><!--[if supportFields]><u><sup><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312'><span style='mso-element:field-begin'></span> = 5 \* GB3 <span
style='mso-element:field-separator'></span></span></sup></u><![endif]-->
<u><sup><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">⑤</span></sup></u><!--[if supportFields]><u><sup><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312'><span style='mso-element:field-end'></span></span></sup></u><![endif]-->
<span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">，大家胳膊、腿脚的动作跟不上，于是她详细耐心地给我们说明纠正，我们的舞跳得渐渐好起来。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:110%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">正式演出的那一天，我们在迪斯科舞厅演出了。听说是迪斯科的老板请我们去跳的。表演成功了。看起来她们有点儿紧张，但是真了不起，看的客人也很多。她们表演的时候，我拍了很多照片。这件事在我心中留下深刻的印象。我非常感激她们让我参加了这个活动。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:110%"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">表演结束了，练习也就完了。我的身体渐渐地适应了跳舞的状态，却没有舞伴一起跳了。我觉得很遗憾，我希望以后再有跳舞的机会。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
仿宋_GB2312"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;
text-indent:24.0pt;line-height:110%"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">&nbsp;<o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoPlainText"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family:黑体">[评改]：<o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoPlainText" style="text-indent:18.6pt">本文截取生活的一个小片断，用跳舞这个事例反映了在中国的外国留学生丰富多彩的留学生活，读来有趣。</p>
<p class="MsoPlainText" style="text-indent:18.6pt">以下几个句子建议作如下的修改：</p>
<p class="MsoPlainText">①“挥动指挥棒跳舞的俱乐部”表意不清楚，去掉，改成：“高中的时候，我非常喜欢跳舞。”</p>
<p class="MsoPlainText">②可改成：“我从宿舍的窗户向外一看”</p>
<p class="MsoPlainText">③这句的“想”改成“看”，“ 看”表示估计、猜测。</p>
<span style="font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">④⑤</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;
mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">“</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;
mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">速度</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">”</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">改成</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;
mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">“</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;
mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">节奏</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:
10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">”</span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-hansi-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-ansi-language:
EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">。<span style="mso-spacerun: yes" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
</span></span><span style="font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:楷体_GB2312;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA">（评改教师：汪志远）</span>

                    
